{"tid":1220980,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"【推上熱門】為支持警察用武力鎮壓學生既洗頭仔宣傳生意","createTime":"2019-06-14T06:10:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T14:22:38.000Z","uid":8830,"like":105,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"b0dae1318f6ab819dce8e91434955d8de6f2ebf9","tid":1220980,"uid":8830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T06:10:46.000Z","msg":"借朋友AC出POST<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最近發現左一個支持警察用武力鎮壓既人士<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>認為用催淚彈 橡膠彈係太仁慈呀</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n7MfYsK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn7MfYsK.jpg&h=8687e34a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>即刻睇下佢係咩人先 我要支持佢</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>  <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ivDaNmn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FivDaNmn.jpg&h=272541f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">原來佢做緊髮型生意架</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CvqwwN5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCvqwwN5.jpg&h=d569542d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我呢D愛國愛港愛香港警察既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇佢到咁支持真係好想幫佢宣傳下呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢身邊既靚仔靚女髮型唔知係咪出自佢手呢<br />\n真係男既英 女既正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fh7fd16.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFh7fd16.jpg&h=c201a83d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vJwWHVs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvJwWHVs.jpg&h=6f6cf2a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CVu9itN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCVu9itN.jpg&h=926d609f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0RU1T18.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0RU1T18.jpg&h=051f71fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/puWPitO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpuWPitO.jpg&h=5857cb8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n工作既樣好有型添呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R5WonVK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR5WonVK.jpg&h=b8d3e62d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果大家有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就快D聯絡佢喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" cla